---
// MTG 3D Prints - Project Landing Page
// A clean, fantasy-inspired tool-oriented design
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Custom MTG 3D Prints | Master Your Boardstate</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Cinzel:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #c5a059; /* Muted Gold/Brass */
            --bg-dark: #121212;
            --bg-card: #1e1e1e;
            --text-light: #e0e0e0;
            --accent: #4a5568;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-light);
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url('https://placehold.co/1200x800/222/444');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #a0aec0;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* --- Buttons --- */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: #000;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #d4b475;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* --- About/Features Section --- */
        .section {
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .feature-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .about-text h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .custom-options {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .custom-options li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .custom-options i {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* --- Contact Form --- */
        .contact-box {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--primary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #2d2d2d;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            height: 120px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #2d2d2d;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content container">
                <h1>Master Your Boardstate</h1>
                <p>Custom 3D-printed tokens, counters, and tactical tools designed for the modern planeswalker.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn">Start a Custom Order</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x600/222/primary?text=Custom+Tokens" alt="3D Printed Tokens" class="feature-img" />
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <h2>Precision Crafted Tools</h2>
                        <p>Ditch the dice and messy boardstates. I create durable, high-visibility accessories that make tracking your game effortless.</p>
                        
                        <ul class="custom-options">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-palette"></i> <strong>Custom Colors:</strong> Match your deck's color identity.</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-pen-nib"></i> <strong>Engraved Text:</strong> Custom labels on cases and token boxes.</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> <strong>Tabletop Ready:</strong> Designed to withstand heavy play and travel.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Form Section -->
        <section id="contact" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="contact-box">
                    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Inquiry Form</h2>
                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">Tell me what you're looking for and let's build your kit.</p>
                    
                    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/your-id-here" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Urza" required />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Email</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="planeswalker@magic.com" required />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Tool Type</label>
                            <select name="type">
                                <option value="tokens">Token Set</option>
                                <option value="counters">+1/+1 Counters</option>
                                <option value="cases">Custom Cases/Boxes</option>
                                <option value="other">Full Custom Project</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Customization Details (Text, Colors, etc.)</label>
                            <textarea name="message" placeholder="I need a set of 10 Soldier tokens in white, with 'Commander 2024' on the box..."></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn" style="width: 100%;">Send Inquiry</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2026 ItsJustIvan  Project. Not affiliated with Wizards of the Coast.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>